The total counting of the vote may also be carried out if at the end of the ordinary counting it is established that the difference between the alleged winner and the second-placed candidate is equal to or less than one percentage point, provided that there is an express request from the representative of the political party whose candidate was in second place, in which case the electoral packages that have been subject to partial counting will be excluded.
